# Excel Week 1 — IT Incident Log Foundation

Date: April 2, 2026
Tool: Microsoft Excel

## Tasks Completed
* Created `IT_Incident_Log.xlsx` with standard Help Desk headers.
* Applied `Freeze Top Row` to maintain header visibility during data scrolling.
* Formatted Header Row: Bold text and Fill Color for visual hierarchy.
* Populated 5 rows of simulated IT ticket data (Hardware, Software, Network).
* Optimized data entry using Tab/Enter keyboard navigation.

## Key Concepts
* `Freeze Panes`: Essential for managing large datasets/logs.
* `Data Type Consistency`: Ensuring the 'Resolution Time' column remains numeric for Week 2 formulas.
* `UI/UX`: Using contrast (background colors) to separate metadata from raw data.

## Lessons Learned
* Manual data entry speed is significantly improved by minimizing mouse usage.
* Pre-formatting columns prevents errors when scaling the log later.

